{"tid":1614773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"優品360年度收入10.76億元","createTime":"2019-10-03T01:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:10:35.000Z","uid":118465,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2033ebb3ce30bf826a60a91bfa09ee5c417ba5cc","tid":1614773,"uid":118465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_646809_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_646809_0&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7MRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=92346d94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_646809_0&h=bacce400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_646809_0</a><br />\n<br />\n股市低迷，759阿信屋「縮鋪」，優品360（2360）上市招股，計劃未來4年擴張76間分店。以招股價上限1.2元計，市值已達12億元，比759阿信屋市值大3倍。優品360於2013年成立，售賣主要較大超市廉宜的大牌子水貨零食，初期主打遊客生意，近日稱未來新店選址以做街坊生意為主。據初步招股文件，截至3月底優品360共有70間分店，年度收入10.76億元，按年升55.93%，盈利5359.9萬元，按年升1.13倍。<br />\n<br />\n一間被破壞仲要無搶野, 對於咁大生意黎講真係零頭黎, 影響唔到咩既"},{"pid":"90156e1767d7790fcfac8b3c49c9353d38bb8513","tid":1614773,"uid":265959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:39:13.000Z","msg":"琴日行過樓下間360冇開鋪"},{"pid":"84489c7d43d52db79281786f9407ff7919f880cc","tid":1614773,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"每年賺10億黎打香港人<br />\n今年開始要蝕10億"},{"pid":"72eacf1208bf03bbe5cd18e6e74bf1cb41d459b6","tid":1614773,"uid":126366,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"依間垃圾 都無見過人入去買嘢 撚有10億 係咪又洗緊黑錢"},{"pid":"28f588e7d6f1beb9c908fe80c9a768ce338e5f00","tid":1614773,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"福建幫 生意"},{"pid":"20acbc13e2d9e903a7b8c56fbeb53223ffe42a88","tid":1614773,"uid":18608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T01:47:17.000Z","msg":"幫福建老洗黑